              '<div class="container-left">\n<h2 dir="ltr">Key Features of the Course</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation"><strong>300+</strong> Unique AWS Cloud Practitioner practice exam Questions with Detailed Explanations</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">AWS Cloud Practitioner Final Test questions are the subset of Practice Tests and Section Tests questions.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation"><strong>14+ hours</strong> of Training Videos (<strong>112 Lectures</strong>) for all Exam Objectives (<strong>100%</strong> Syllabus Covered)</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"><strong>9+ </strong>Section Quiz on Topic wise questions from Cloud Practitioner\'s latest exam version</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation"><strong>72</strong> labs for the AWS Cloud Practitioner Exam (CLF-C02)</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Unlimited access for <strong>2</strong> years</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Detailed videos on all the topics and sub-topics</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation"><strong>24/7</strong> Subject Matter Expert&rsquo;s support</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Auto-updates to the course content<br><br></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="readmore">\n<h2 class="title">What you\'ll learn as a beginner in the AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner (CLF-C02) Certification Course?</h2>\n<p>If you are a beginner in AWS Cloud and trying to attempt the AWS Cloud Practitioner CLF-C02 exam, you will be learning on:</p>\n<ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Managing the infrastructure of AWS cloud and values of AWS Cloud</li>\n<li>Cloud Architecture principles of AWS Cloud</li>\n<li>The shared security model and compliance concepts in AWS</li>\n<li>Technical assistance / documentation</li>\n<li>Account management, billing,&nbsp;pricing and support in AWS</li>\n<li>Use cases and AWS services</li>\n<li>AWS Cloud Deployment &amp; Operation</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<p>It is highly recommended to start with AWS Learning Plan. Becoming a certified AWS professional opens up numerous opportunities in the cloud computing industry.<br><br></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">Requirements Before Taking the AWS Cloud Practitioner Exam (CLF-C02)</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">You do not have to have prior experience with AWS to take the <strong>AWS Cloud Practitioner Exam.</strong> It is suitable for individuals who are new to cloud computing.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Candidates with basic experience in AWS can upskill themselves by attempting this exam. Some of the requirements before attempting the <strong>AWS Cloud Practitioner Exam</strong> are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">A minimum of 6 months of practical experience working with the AWS cloud platform.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Exposure to cloud design, implementation, and operations</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Basic understanding of Core AWS Cloud Services</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">AWS Security and compliance</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Knowledge of handling AWS economics</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir="ltr">Have clear exam objectives from the video courses. Try our updated AWS Cloud Certified Practitioner practice exam and learn the topics where you need to improvise yourself.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">This way, you can take the exam with a fearless approach and earn your certificate on your first attempt. The exam expects only the basic skills of an AWS beginner.</p>\n<h2 class="title">&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2 dir="ltr">Who Should Take The AWS Cloud Practitioner Certification Exam?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Non-IT background and those who want to explore a career in the AWS Cloud</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Sales/marketing/business analysts who are seeking to communicate effectively with the stakeholders and customers about the AWS Cloud</p>\n</li>\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">On-premises IT or cloud roles, but new to AWS Cloud, and require a primer before taking role-based AWS certifications.<br><br><br></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir="ltr">The Ultimate <span data-sheets-root="1">AWS Cloud Practitioner Certification Exam</span>&nbsp;Benefits</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">No matter what role you are playing in AWS as an entry-level, this certification can boost your career to an advanced level. Obtaining an AWS certification can significantly boost your career prospects in the field of cloud computing.</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir="ltr" role="presentation"><strong>AWS Career for Freshers:<br></strong>The Amazon Web Services entry-level certification helps you secure job placements in the growing AWS cloud computing industry. You may start learning the AWS CCP course and pass the exam to pursue your dream career.<br><br></li>\n<li dir="ltr" role="presentation"><strong>Career Upgradation:<br></strong>If you are in an AWS project, an AWS CCP certificate can promote you to the next level and stabilize your career growth.&nbsp;<br><br>The AWS certification exam preparation is highly suitable for those who want to enter the cloud industry. Taking AWS training can help you gain the skills and recognition needed to excel in cloud computing.<strong id="docs-internal-guid-78b631a7-7fff-91da-5e01-a06d53be8c4f"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-11fdee7f-7fff-4ea0-2db4-97e597438c54"></strong></strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>',
